QueryText: ASKING FOR THE MANAGEMENT OF BLAST DISEASE OF RICE.
KCCAns: I SUGGEST HIM TO SPRAY CARBENDAZIM @ 2g PER LITRE OF WATER.

QueryText: ASKING ABOUT THE CONTROL MEASURE PLANT HOPPER IN RICE.
KCCAns:
SUGGESTED TO SPRAY FIPRONIL @ 2GM/LT OF WATER OR IMIDACLOPRID @ 7ML/15 LT OF WATER OR CLOTHIANIDIN 
50% WDG (Dantotsu)@6GM/90LT OF WATER.
